<p><strong>旅者，又名传道士</strong></p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3967806&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781489" alt="ShineShadowD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3967806)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;">ShineShadowD</a></span></p>
