<p><strong>图片信息：</strong></p>
<p>画廊：<br />
来自<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simon-arran" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4354147); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4354147&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606781489" alt="Simon Arran" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4354147)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simon-arran" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4354147); return false;">Simon Arran</a></span> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/gallery/The-Great-Dragon-Spine.jpg">http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/gallery/The-Great-Dragon-Spine.jpg</a></p>
<hr />
